Complaints
If you wish to complain about a product or service, please send us an e-mail to shop@donebydeer.com.
Make sure to include a photo of the product and your order number, in order for us to help you as fast as possible.

If you feel that your problem has not be resolved, you can send a complaint to:

For Danish citizens:
Nævnenes Hus, Toldboden, 8800 Viborg, Denmark, https://naevneneshus.dk/

For European citizens outside of Denmark: please send your complaint to EU Commission’s online complaints portal here – http://ec.europa.eu/odr.
